{
  "texts": [
    "The mathematical Eq. 7 for the accuracy is given by (Zidi et al., 2023):",
    "Increasing the True Positive Rate (TPR), Fraud Detection Rate (FDR), and low false positive rate is the main goal of ETD (Jindal et al., 2016).",
    "To detect NTLs using binary classification, the ROC-AUC is a suitable metric.",
    "To create it, TPR, also known as recall, is plotted against false positive rate while the decision thresholds are being adjusted.",
    "The range of the score is 0-1."
  ]
}